{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/game-augmented-reality-harry-potter-akan-segera-dirilis-tahun-depan/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Game Augmented Reality Harry Potter Akan Segera Dirilis Tahun Depan!","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Niantic Inc sepertinya belajar banyak dari kesuksesan Pokemon GO beberapa tahun lalu. Tak berhenti sampai di situ saja, sempat sukses “memporak-porandakan” dunia lewat game berbasis <em>Augmented Reality</em>-nya, kini sepertinya Niantic kembali ingin menyabet popularitas lewat game terbarunya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_28157\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-28157\" data-attachment-id=\"28157\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-augmented-reality-harry-potter-akan-segera-dirilis-tahun-depan/attachment/isi-1-84/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-26.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Rumornya dulu nama game Harry Potter GO. Sumber: Did you know facts\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Rumornya dulu nama game Harry Potter GO. Sumber: Did you know facts&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-26.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-26.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28157\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-1-26.jpg\" alt=\"Rumornya dulu nama game Harry Potter GO. Sumber: Did you know facts\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-28157\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Rumornya dulu nama game Harry Potter GO. Sumber: Did you know facts</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Masih mengusung tema <em>Augmented Reality</em>, Niantic Inc yang bekerja sama dengan Warner Bros akan membuat game Harry Potter versi AR. Dengan mengusung nama Harry Potter: Wizard Unite, Niantic digadang-gadang akan kembali menuai kesuksesan besar seperti di era Pokemon GO.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_28169\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-28169\" data-attachment-id=\"28169\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-augmented-reality-harry-potter-akan-segera-dirilis-tahun-depan/attachment/isi-5-61/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-5-20.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Seorang youtuber mem-videokan area Central Park yang diramaikan oleh para pemburu pokemon. Sumber: youtube\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Seorang youtuber mem-videokan area Central Park yang diramaikan oleh para pemburu pokemon. Sumber: youtube&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-5-20.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-5-20.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28169\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-5-20.jpg\" alt=\"Seorang youtuber mem-videokan area Central Park yang diramaikan oleh para pemburu pokemon. Sumber: youtube\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-28169\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Seorang Youtuber mem-videokan area Central Park yang diramaikan oleh para pemburu Pokemon. Sumber: youtube</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Konsepnya masih sama, yaitu, game AR yang <em>collab</em> dengan <em>franchise</em> populer, yang kali ini adalah Harry Potter. Tentunya ini merupakan kabar baik bagi para pembaca setia novel besutan JK. Rowling tersebut. Game ini dapat menjadi kesempatan bagi para fans untuk dapat menikmati dunia sihir hasil imajinatif JK. Rowling secara lebih ‘<em>real</em>’.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_28160\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-28160\" data-attachment-id=\"28160\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-augmented-reality-harry-potter-akan-segera-dirilis-tahun-depan/attachment/isi-2-78/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-2-26.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: hypable\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: hypable&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-2-26.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-2-26.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28160\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-2-26.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: hypable\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-28160\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: hypable</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Niantic masih belum menginformasikan tanggal resmi perilisan game tersebut. Namun yang pasti, game ini akan segera dirilis tahun 2018.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sebenarnya isu Niantic akan membuat game AR Harry Potter ini sudah terdengar sejak tahun lalu. Sayangnya rumor tersebut dibantah habis-habisan. Mungkin pihak developer masih belum mau memberi &#8216;harapan palsu&#8217; kepada paran fans. Sehingga baru minggu ini, lewat laman resminya, Niantic baru memberi pernyataan resmi mengenai game ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_28184\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-28184\" data-attachment-id=\"28184\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-augmented-reality-harry-potter-akan-segera-dirilis-tahun-depan/attachment/screen-shot-2017-11-20-at-4-48-39-pm/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-20-at-4.48.39-PM.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: nianticlabs\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: nianticlabs&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-20-at-4.48.39-PM.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-20-at-4.48.39-PM.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28184\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/Screen-Shot-2017-11-20-at-4.48.39-PM.png\" alt=\"Sumber: nianticlabs\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-28184\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: nianticlabs</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lewat blognya di nianticlabs.com, sang CEO, John Hanke membeberkan sedikit <em>hint</em> dari <em>gameplay</em> Harry Potter: Wizard Unite. Hanya bermodalkan <em>smartphone,</em> kita dapat berpetualang menjelajahi wilayah sekitar kita, membangun karir sebagai penyihir, mencari <em>magical creature</em> dan bertemu dengan tokoh-tokoh ikonik yang ada di dalam film Harry Potter. Dalam game ini, pemain juga bisa mempelajari mantra, bersembunyi serta harus berhadapan dan mengalahkan makhluk-makhluk berbahaya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_28163\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-28163\" data-attachment-id=\"28163\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-augmented-reality-harry-potter-akan-segera-dirilis-tahun-depan/attachment/isi-3-76/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-26.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Siapkah bro sis memasuki dunia Harry Potter? Sumber: JuiceOnline\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Siapkah bro sis memasuki dunia Harry Potter? Sumber: JuiceOnline&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-26.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-26.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28163\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-3-26.jpg\" alt=\"Siapkah bro sis memasuki dunia Harry Potter? Sumber: JuiceOnline\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-28163\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Siapkah bro sis memasuki dunia Harry Potter? Sumber: JuiceOnline</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kolaborasi antara Warner Bros, Interactive Entertainment dan Niantic Inc, turut membuat David Haddad, presiden dari Warner Bros sangat semangat dan tidak sabar memainkan game AR Harry Potter: Wizard Unite. “Dengan game ini, kita memberikan kesempatan kepada para fans berat Harry Potter di seluruh dunia untuk mengeksplor lebih dalam dan nyata dunia yang JK. Rowling ciptakan.” kata David Haddad.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_28166\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-28166\" data-attachment-id=\"28166\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-augmented-reality-harry-potter-akan-segera-dirilis-tahun-depan/attachment/isi-4-75/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-4-26.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Niantic X Warner Bros\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-4-26.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-4-26.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28166\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/isi-4-26.jpg\" alt=\"Niantic X Warner Bros\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-28166\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Niantic X Warner Bros</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Untuk info detail lain mengenai Harry Potter, kabarnya akan diumumkan pada tahun 2018 mendatang. Gimana bro sis, sudah siap menjelajahi dunia Harry Potter tahun depan?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"b7bb0caa-e2c4-59be-9455-4d069b096f2b"}}}